# NEU Library Visitor Log System

A web-based library visitor tracking system for New Era University.

## 🔗 Live Demo
https://neu-library-rho.vercel.app

## 📋 Features

### For Visitors (Students/Faculty/Staff)
- Register with NEU institutional email
- Log in and select reason for visit
- View personal visit history
- Exit library to record time out

### For Admin
- View visitor statistics (daily/weekly/monthly)
- Search visitors by name, role, or reason
- Filter by date range
- Block/unblock users
- Export visitor report to PDF
- View currently inside library
- Manage all registered users

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Supabase (Database)
- Vercel (Hosting)
- GitHub (Version Control)

## 📁 Project Structure
```
InfoMa2/
├── adminLogin/     → Admin login page
├── adminPage/      → Admin dashboard
├── dboard/         → User dashboard
├── Login/          → User login page
├── Registration/   → Registration page
├── WelcomPage/     → Welcome + reason page
└── supabase.js     → Database connection
```

## 🗄️ Database Tables

### users
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | uuid | Primary key |
| email | text | NEU email |
| password | text | User password |
| first_name | text | First name |
| last_name | text | Last name |
| role | text | student/faculty/staff/admin |
| college | text | For students |
| department | text | For faculty |
| position | text | For staff |
| is_blocked | boolean | Block status |

### visits
| Column | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id     | uuid | Primary key |
|user_id | uuid | Reference to users |
| reason | text | Visit reason |
|time_in | timestamp | Entry time |
|time_out| timestamp | Exit time |
| date   | date | Visit date |

## 👤 Default Admin Credentials
- Email: admin@neu.edu.ph
- Password: admin1234

## 🚀 How to Run Locally
1. Clone the repository
2. Open with VS Code
3. Install Live Server extension
4. Open `Login/login.html` with Live Server

